+# AI Learning Assistant 🚀
+
+## Features
+- AI Tutor
+- Knowledge Gap Detection
+- Learning Path Generator
+- RAG-based responses
+
+## Run
+```bash
+mvn spring-boot:run
+```
+
+## APIs
+POST /api/learning/ask  
+POST /api/learning/assess  
+GET /api/learning/path/{userId}
